    <p>Sun­down­ers At Spago Bar & Lounge</p>
    <p>Catch the sun­set at Spago Bar & Lounge while en­joy­ing the al­fresco venue’s Sun­down­ers menu. Light bites in­clude sushi (from $16++).</p>
    <p>Pair them with Spago’s in­no­va­tive cock­tails such as the Gar­den of Eden ($19++), a blend of mango black tea-in­fused vodka with lemon and a touch of cane su­gar, or a re­fresh­ing Zef­fer Red Ap­ple Cider. Pours by the glass are also avail­able.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Spago Bar & Lounge, Level 57 Sands Sky­Park, Ho­tel Tower 2, 10 Bayfront Av­enue MRT: Bayfront</p>
    <p>WHEN: 4 - 7pm daily PRICE: From $16++ for sushi TEL: 6688-9955</p>
    <p>INFO: www.marin­abaysands.com/ restau­rants/spago-barand-lounge.html</p>


